  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/8e97ceb6ec329c36d5d9f9ddec91c907.avif?t=1746026398\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl 2</strong> lets you duke it out with the biggest and best fighting character roster yet, including all new characters like SpongeBob SquarePants, Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles, Squidward Tentacles, Jimmy Neutron, and more!<br><br>Choose your favorite brawlers, master their unique move sets, and use all-new powerful Supers to land the finishing blow with friends or across a unique, roguelike player campaign!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/a43c0216a694946d879b0fe02733e979.poster.avif?t=1746026398\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/a43c0216a694946d879b0fe02733e979.webm?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/a43c0216a694946d879b0fe02733e979.mp4?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Featuring:<br>• <strong>New Single-Player Campaign:</strong> Put your skills to the test as you fight to stop Danny Phantom archvillain Vlad Plasmius from taking over the Nickelodeon universe!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/6aa2e09ea342a57734d26592da4b5cf4.poster.avif?t=1746026398\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/6aa2e09ea342a57734d26592da4b5cf4.webm?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/6aa2e09ea342a57734d26592da4b5cf4.mp4?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• <strong>All-New Gameplay:</strong> New and revamped visuals meets new audio, animations, modes, stages, mechanics, taunts and move sets for all levels of play!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/b43038e56453caf7618a0c7bd0425a2a.poster.avif?t=1746026398\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/b43038e56453caf7618a0c7bd0425a2a.webm?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/b43038e56453caf7618a0c7bd0425a2a.mp4?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• <strong>Cinematic Supers:</strong> Power up your fighters with incredible new animated supers to deal devastating blows to your opponents!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/aa98f07269bc0a7c430ca4176d488093.poster.avif?t=1746026398\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/aa98f07269bc0a7c430ca4176d488093.webm?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/aa98f07269bc0a7c430ca4176d488093.mp4?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• <strong>New & Improved Brawlers:</strong> Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl 2’s roster is better than ever, with even more variety in how each unique character plays. Battle with brand new Nickelodeon fighters as well as returning fan favorites!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/b584f079085482d95c9dfc5cf6e076cf.poster.avif?t=1746026398\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/b584f079085482d95c9dfc5cf6e076cf.webm?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017080/extras/b584f079085482d95c9dfc5cf6e076cf.mp4?t=1746026398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
